873" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3805873" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3805873" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Springsteen@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Springsteen@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Springsteen@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Springsteen@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Springsteen@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Springsteen@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Springsteen@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3805873" class="wp-caption-text">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀 (Bruce Springsteen) 将于 2024 年演出。（摄影：Mariano Regidor/Redferns/Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>斯普林斯汀<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-to-headline-kamala-harris-rallies-in-atlanta-and-philadelphia-3805409">接下来将于周一（10 月 28 日）出席哈里斯在费城的集会</a>。</p><p>斯普林斯汀的音乐长期以来一直带有政治色彩，但他首次公开支持总统是在 2008 年，当时他宣布支持奥巴马。此后，他在 2016 年支持希拉里·克林顿，在 2020 年支持乔·拜登，甚至为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-narrates-joe-biden-campaign-advertisement-2806054">他的竞选广告做</a>旁白，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-perform-land-of-hope-and-dreams-during-joe-biden-inauguration-tv-special-celebrating-america-2861628">在 2021 年初的就职典礼上表演</a>。</p><p>其他支持哈里斯的名人包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-endorsement-of-kamala-harris-for-president-3792514">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-john-legend-and-more-endorse-kamala-harris-for-us-president-3776745">查理·XCX</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">查普尔·罗恩</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonces-