阿根廷警方突袭利亚姆·佩恩死亡酒店https://www.nme.com/news/music/argentinian-police-raid-hotel-where-liam-payne-died-3806078?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=argentinian-police-raid-hotel-where-liam-佩恩去世Surej SinghFri, 25 Oct 2024 02:09:17 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3806078 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>寻找更多证据，包括硬盘、安全摄像机镜头和文档</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/argentinian-police-raid-hotel-where-liam-payne-died-3806078">阿根廷警方突袭利亚姆·佩恩死亡酒店</a>后的情况首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，阿根廷当局对上周<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-payne">利亚姆·佩恩</a>死亡的布宜诺斯艾利斯酒店进行了突袭。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/liam-payne-one-direction-obituary-3803755">Liam Payne 1993-2024：单向明星帮助引发了流行现象</a></strong></li></ul><p>上周三（10月16日），有消息称，这位独唱艺人、前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/one-direction">One Direction</a>成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-directions-liam-payne-had-died-aged-31-3803523">从阿根廷布宜诺斯艾利斯卡萨苏尔巴勒莫酒店三楼阳台坠落</a>不幸身亡，年仅31岁。阿根廷检察官办公室随后表示，他的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-cause-of-death-and-details-of-hotel-room-in-disarray-revealed-3803859">死因是多处外伤和内外出血</a>。</p><p>本周早些时候，据报道，佩恩<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-payne-reportedly-had-pink-cocaine-and-other-substances-in-his-system-at-time-of-death-3804922">在阳台坠落身亡时，体内有粉红可卡因和其他几种物质</a>。消息人士告诉<a href="https://abcnews.go.com/GMA/Culture/liam-payne-partial-autopsy-report-multiple-substances/story?id=114985701" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>美国广播公司新闻</em></a>，部分尸检结果显示，他体内含有“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/colombias-pink-cocaine-reportedly-spreading-through-europe-3365579">粉红色可卡因</a>”——一种通常由甲基苯丙胺、氯胺酮、摇头丸等物质混合而成的药物——以及可卡因、苯二氮卓类药物和快克。报道还称，从他当时入住的酒店房间中发现了一根临时铝管。 </p><figure id="attachment_3804331" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3804331" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3804331" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne-jc-olivera-1.jpg" alt="利亚姆·佩恩" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne-jc-olivera-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne-jc-olivera-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne-jc-olivera-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne-jc-olivera-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne-jc-olivera-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne-jc-olivera-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3804331" class="wp-caption-text"> 2022 年的利亚姆·佩恩。（摄影：JC Olivera/Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>现在，当地新闻网站<a href="https://www.lanacion.com.ar/seguridad/liam-payne-la-policia-de-la-ciudad-allana-el-hotel-desde-donde-murio-el-ex-one-direction-nid23102024/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>La Nacion</em></a>报道称，布宜诺斯艾利斯警察局已突击搜查 CasaSur 酒店，以寻找进一步的证据。消息人士告诉该报，他们专门寻找文件、电影记录和视频，以帮助拼凑出这位已故歌手生命的最后几个小时。</p><p> <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/music/2024/oct/24/argentinian-police-raid-liam-payne-hotel" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报》</em></a>还报道称，迄今为止参与活动的查获物品包括电脑硬盘和酒店的监控录像。此外， <em>《国家报》</em>指出，已对酒店工作人员以及几名当局成员进行了进一步采访，其中包括参与此案的技术和医疗专业人员。</p><p>此次突击搜查是由法官劳拉·布鲁尼亚德和安德烈斯·马德雷亚下令进行的，后者是检察官办公室的案件负责人。据<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/buenos-aires-police-raid-hotel-liam-payne-1235141790/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石杂志</em></a>报道，检察官办公室的目标是对突袭期间查获的手机、电脑、照片、安全录像和所有其他形式的证据进行法医测试。</p><p>这次突袭是在利亚姆的父亲杰夫·佩恩上周<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-father-reads-fan-tributes-outside-argentinian-hotel-where-he-died-3804283">抵达布宜诺斯艾利斯协助调查</a>之后进行的。他要求马德雷亚和检察官办公室全面调查利亚姆的死亡，同时等待完整的毒理学和尸检报告，之后他将把他儿子的尸体带回英国。 </p><figure id="attachment_3805683" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3805683" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3805683" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3805683" class="wp-caption-text">利亚姆·佩恩.图片来源：Andrew Chin/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>佩恩的惨死引发了关于为年轻艺术家提供更多保护的讨论，歌曲作家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/guy-chambers-calls-on-the-music-industry-to-stop-putting-teenagers-in-pop-groups-following-liam-paynes-death-3804414">盖伊·钱伯斯在他去世后呼吁音乐产业停止让未成年人加入男孩乐队</a>。佩恩第一次参加<em>《X Factor》</em>试镜时年仅 14 岁，在节目第 10 季期间成为 One Direction 成员时年仅 16 岁。</p><p>在其他地方，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Sharon-Osbourne">莎朗·奥斯本</a>也<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sharon-osbourne-accuses-music-industry-of-letting-down-liam-payne-3803983">指责音乐产业“让佩恩失望”</a> ，她在 Instagram 上发帖写道：“利亚姆，我的心很痛。我们都让你失望了。当你需要他们的时候这个行业在哪里？当你进入世界上最艰难的行业之一时，你还只是个孩子。谁在你的角落里？安息吧我的朋友。”</p><p>与 One Direction 一起参加选秀节目的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Katie-Waissel">凯蒂·维塞尔 (Katie Waissel</a> ) 此后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/katie-waissel-calls-for-more-care-and-support-for-young-artists-after-death-of-liam-payne-the-focus-remained-on-profits-rather-than-the-people-3803888">呼吁更多“对年轻艺术家的关心和支持</a>”。同样，在同一季节目中获得第二名的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rebecca-ferguson">丽贝卡·弗格森</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rebecca-ferguson-speaks-out-on-exploitation-and-profiteering-of-young-stars-in-liam-payne-tribute-3803708">在向佩恩致敬的同时，也公开反对“对年轻明星的剥削和牟取暴利”。</a> </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-bieber-empathises-with-fans-following-liam-paynes-death-you-are-allowed-to-grieve-3804961"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀还表示，佩恩去世后，音乐产业“给年轻人带来了巨大的压力”，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Victoria-Canal">维多利亚·卡纳尔</a>也表示， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/victoria-canal-on-the-lethality-of-the-internet-and-liam-payne-just-days-before-his-death-liam-was-relentlessly-torn-apart-online-for-dancing-at-niall-horans-show-3804204">作为一名“绝望”想要实现佩恩曾经取得的成功的艺术家，感觉被欺骗了“这个行业‘成功’的承诺是什么。”</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-death-petition-safeguarding-mental-health-artists-3805132">此后发起了一份新的请愿书，呼吁制定新的法律来保障音乐行业艺术家的心理健康</a>。请愿书已获得超过10万签名。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/argentinian-police-raid-hotel-where-liam-payne-died-3806078">阿根廷警方突袭利亚姆·佩恩死亡酒店</a>后的情况首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
聆听 Damiano David 令人振奋的新单曲“Born With A Broken Heart” https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-damiano-davids-uplifting-new-single-born-with-a-broken-heart-3806083?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=listen-to-达米亚诺·戴维斯令人振奋的新单身出生与破碎的心Surej SinghFri, 25 Oct 2024 01:41:10 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3806083 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/damiano-david@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/damiano-david@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/damiano-david@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/damiano-david@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/damiano-david@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/damiano-david@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/damiano-david@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这是 Måneskin 主唱即将推出的个人专辑的第二次尝试</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-damiano-davids-uplifting-new-single-born-with-a-broken-heart-3806083">聆听 Damiano David 令人振奋的新单曲“Born With A Broken Heart”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/damiano-david@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/damiano-david@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/damiano-david@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/damiano-david@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/damiano-david@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/damiano-david@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/damiano-david@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/damiano-david">达米亚诺·大卫 (Damiano David)</a>发行了他令人振奋、充满活力的新单曲《生来破碎的心》——您可以在下面收听。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/maneskin-damiano-david-inteview-silverlines-solo-album-band-future-3797604">Måneskin 的 Damiano David 在《Silverlines》中独唱：“我基本上让自己不开心，但我做得很好”</a></strong></li></ul><p>今天（10 月 25 日），这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/maneskin">Måneskin</a>主唱为歌迷们带来了他即将推出的个人专辑的第二次体验，该专辑尚未确定发行日期。 《Born With A Broken Heart》将令人愉悦的摇滚乐和赞美诗的和弦进行与取自歌手生命中深深的个人和黑暗时期的凄美而感人的歌词融为一体。</p><p>大卫在这首歌朗朗上口的副歌中唱道：“<em>如果我说我正在努力/为了拯救你的爱免于死亡/宝贝我已经走得太远了/不想看到你哭泣/但我只知道我是谁/怎么办？也许这是最难的部分/宝贝你无法修复我/我生来就有一颗破碎的心”</em> 。</p><p>下面请听达米亚诺·大卫 (Damiano David) 的《生来破碎的心》。 </p><p><iframe title="Spotify 嵌入：生来就有一颗破碎的心" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="352" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/2QNTqojFg0R17Jn2gj9Yqm?si=Yh_ZJ3P8TyOkGq2y9sLLMg&#038;utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p>大卫在一份新闻声明中谈到这首新歌时说：“当我写这首歌时，我正走出一个非常黑暗的地方，我感觉毫无感情，我担心我已经失去了感受事物的能力，无论是好还是坏。这件事发生在我开始一生中最有意义的关系时，我对自己没有能力或没有准备好感到非常恐惧。”</p><p> “我认为这首歌是让自己理解自己的感受并从不那么可怕的角度看待它的一种方式，”他继续说道。 “我很高兴地说，今天我没有这样的感觉，但我认为很多人都能体会到“不够好”的感觉。”</p><p>新发行的单曲的随附音乐视频将于今天晚些时候（10 月 25 日）中午 12 点（英国夏令时）发布。 </p><figure id="attachment_3794888" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3794888" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3794888" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ManeskinDamianoDavid-launches-solo-project-announces-debut-single-Silverlines.jpg" alt="Måneskin 的 Damiano David 的新闻图片" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ManeskinDamianoDavid-launches-solo-project-announces-debut-single-Silverlines.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ManeskinDamianoDavid-launches-solo-project-announces-debut-single-Silverlines-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ManeskinDamianoDavid-launches-solo-project-announces-debut-single-Silverlines-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ManeskinDamianoDavid-launches-solo-project-announces-debut-single-Silverlines-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ManeskinDamianoDavid-launches-solo-project-announces-debut-single-Silverlines-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ManeskinDamianoDavid-launches-solo-project-announces-debut-single-Silverlines-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3794888" class="wp-caption-text"> Måneskin 的达米亚诺·大卫。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>《Born With A Broken Heart》是继达米亚诺于 9 月底推出的大胆戏剧钢琴主导民谣《Silverlines》之后推出的个人首张专辑。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/maneskin-damiano-david-inteview-silverlines-solo-album-band-future-3797604">九月，大卫在接受<em>《NME》</em>采访时谈到了他的个人项目</a>，他谈到了他即将推出的首张专辑：“我想说，这将是非常夸张、非常戏剧化、非常戏剧化的。这绝对是更个性化的。这是关于活着的戏剧；尤其是在这种情况下。”</p><p>然而，大卫也明确表示，仅仅因为 Måneskin 的成员目前正在探索独唱生涯，并不意味着乐队的结束：“我们正在接受训练，以不同、更好、更努力的方式回归。 ”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-damiano-davids-uplifting-new-single-born-with-a-broken-heart-3806083">聆听 Damiano David 令人振奋的新单曲“Born With A Broken Heart”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
